name: The Dragon Quest viii: journey of the cursed king
description:
[PT/BR]Um RPG fantástico, lotado de personagens cativantes e uma trama generica, mas para a epoca foi incrivel!," ue? Dragon Ball ta diferente XD".
[EN/BR]A fantastic RPG, full of captivating characters and a generic plot, but for the time it was amazing!," uh? It's Dragon Ball just weird XD".
